dct_title_s: Shi jie zui xin di tu
dct_description_sm: Shanghai shang wu jin shu guan fa xing. Ancillary maps: Baergan ban dao xin tu, Ao Xuong fen lie tu, Deyizhi Belan he tu, Ouzou xian shi tu. Translation of title: The world newest map. Maritime routes are indicated.
